perl-error: perl-error (Error/exception handling in an OO-ish way)
perl-error:
perl-error: The Error package provides two interfaces. Firstly Error provides a
perl-error: procedural interface to exception handling. Secondly Error is a base
perl-error: class for errors/exceptions that can either be thrown, for subsequent
perl-error: catch, or can simply be recorded.
perl-error:
perl-error: http://search.cpan.org/dist/Error/
